title: Jerry Jones, Baker Mayfield, Bowl games
itunes:title: Jerry Jones, Baker Mayfield, Bowl games
description:
Filling in for Colin Cowherd, Jason McIntyre discusses if and when Cowboys owner Jerry Jones will fire Jason Garrett. What Browns Quarterback Baker Mayfield needs to start doing, and the upcoming College Bowl Games. Guest appear: Albert Breer and John Middlekauff
